  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Here’s a cute, chubby black cat.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All it wants to do is quietly go fishing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“Right in the corner of your desktop!”</strong><br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4042500/extras/b6231044de989782492de97cbff09be9.avif?t=1773993572\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><br><br><br><br><br><br><strong></strong><br><br><br><br><br><br><strong>Collect fish to fill up the cat’s encyclopedia, earn money, and dress it up in adorable outfits!</strong><br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4042500/extras/5b121e969967e5ee52a80b518aca1e8c.avif?t=1773993572\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><strong>Desktop Fishing Cat</strong> is a calm and charming <strong>idle desktop game</strong>. <br>Watch this little <strong>black cat</strong> fish peacefully on your screen and enjoy a soothing moment. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4042500/extras/c55e8195fae17335dfcb01d8642446bd.avif?t=1773993572\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please help this cat...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“Right in the corner of your desktop!”</strong><br><strong></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4042500/extras/803505e91ef91255ae7a19c20d532035.avif?t=1773993572\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >--------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game was inspired by Cornerpond’s systems and the artwork of Illu Finch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
